divs: Sighting Detailsi was making a delivery to the school kitchen.i look up at the sky often because i have seen so many,like over 15 in the past 20 yrs.looked north from school parking lot and saw a very shiny object like the size of jupiter. was going very slow towards the west and ascending into a clear blue sky. saw it for about 10 minutes total.it went up pretty high so that it was just a tiny shiny dot in the sky,it never stopped while i was looking at it.i felt happy to have seen it and can not wait to see the next one.
